r the NHS</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">’</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> which draws together learning from case studies, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">and provides </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">reflections and recommendations </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">that</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> will be of practical use to </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Commissioner</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">Quality Standards for Dermatology</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">providing the right care for people with skin conditions</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">is a </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">multi</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">stakeholder </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">(including the BAD) </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">publication </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">and is available on the PCC website and has implications for commissioning</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">5</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">The ability of NHS to treat multi-morbidities and the patient as a person </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">5.1</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">P</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">atients with skin disease often require treatment for existing co-morbidities </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">(for example psoriasis and </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">metabolic syndrome) </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">by </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">their</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> GP and </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Dermatology</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">and other specialists</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> these patients need to be identified </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">bec</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">a</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">u</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">e</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> they impact on services across the levels of care and </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">a</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">cross specialties.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> A </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">Needs Assessment</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> is therefore a crucial step in drawing up service specifications.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">5.2</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Dermatologist</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s are frequently required </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11p